      <title>日本股票暴跌，因为美国关税担心会击中出口商股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/japanese-shares-plunge-as-us-tariff-worries-hit-exporter-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股票跌落，使Nikkei的股票量规定在2020年3月以来最糟糕的季度，因为与出口相关的股票对全球贸易战的担忧滑落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/japanese-shares-plunge-as-us-tariff-worries-hit-exporter-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 01:04:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国第二钢制造商的年损失近10亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-s-no-2-steelmaker-makes-annual-loss-of-nearly-1-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Angang Steel Co Ltd.是中国第二大钢铁制造商的上市部门，去年亏损了近10亿美元，突显了该行业的洪水条件，因为需求降低和价格涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-s-no-2-steelmaker-makes-annual-loss-of-nearly-1-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 01:02:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>聊天机器人聚合器WRTN获得了最新韩国AI交易的资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/chatbot-aggregator-wrtn-gets-funding-in-latest-korea-ai-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[WRTN Technologies Inc.已从包括Goodwater Capital在内的投资者中筹集了830亿韩元（5600万美元），这是越来越多的韩国人工智能初创公司之一，以在茶几后时代获得融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/chatbot-aggregator-wrtn-gets-funding-in-latest-korea-ai-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 00:52:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
