      <title>害虫，啮齿动物的恐惧继续拖下Zensho股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/pest-rodent-fears-continue-to-drag-down-zensho-shares</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Zensho Holdings Co.的股价下跌了6.5％，此前日本餐厅连锁店表示，在多次食品污染事件发生后，它将暂时关闭其大多数Sukiya商店。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/pest-rodent-fears-continue-to-drag-down-zensho-shares</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 00:38:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
